{"word":"Concealment-Exposure","slug":"concealment-exposure","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Concealment-Exposure</b> - <b>(A) CONCEALMENT OF SIN.</b> the attempt to hide sin from God<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=8'>Gen 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=21'>Jos 7:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=9'>2Ki 17:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=28&verse=13'>Pro 28:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=29&verse=15'>Isa 29:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=30&verse=1'>Isa 30:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8&verse=12'>Eze 8:12</a><p/><b>(B) SECRET SINS</b><p/><b>(1) Warnings Against</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=17&verse=9'>2Ki 17:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=24&verse=16'>Job 24:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=19&verse=12'>Psa 19:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=90&verse=8'>Psa 90:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=29&verse=15'>Isa 29:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8&verse=12'>Eze 8:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=12'>Eph 5:12</a><p/><b>(2) Called Works of Darkness</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=24&verse=14'>Job 24:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=7&verse=8'>Pro 7:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=7&verse=9'>Pro 7:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=20'>Joh 3:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=13&verse=12'>Rom 13:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=11'>Eph 5:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=5&verse=7'>1Th 5:7</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Evil Activity, ACTIVITY, EVIL<p/><b>(C) EXPOSURE OF SIN</b><p/><b>(1) Inevitable</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=32&verse=23'>Num 32:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=20&verse=27'>Job 20:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=26&verse=26'>Pro 26:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=12&verse=14'>Ecc 12:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=2'>Luk 12:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=4&verse=5'>1Co 4:5</a><p/><b>(2) Rendered Doubly Certain</b> by God's Infinite Knowledge<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=10&verse=14'>Job 10:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=14&verse=16'>Job 14:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=2&verse=22'>Jer 2:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=16&verse=17'>Jer 16:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=11&verse=5'>Eze 11:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=7&verse=2'>Hos 7:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=5&verse=12'>Amo 5:12</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Hearts Read, KNOWLEDGE<p/>God's Knowledge, KNOWLEDGE<p/>Omniscience, WISDOM<p/>Divine Vision, VISION<p/> VISION<p/>\"Searcher\", KNOWLEDGE<p/><b>(3) No Matter How Committed,</b> Sin will be Exposed<p/>Like the sin of Cain it may be done in secret<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=4&verse=8'>Ge 4:8-10</a><p/>Like the sin of Esau, it may be done under the impulse of the moment<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=32'>Gen 25:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=33'>Gen 25:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=17'>Gen 25:17</a><p/>Like the sin of Joseph's Brethren, it may be years before its discovery<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42&verse=21'>Ge 42:21</a><p/>Like the sin of Achan, it may be well covered up<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=21'>Jos 7:21</a><p/>Like the sin of Samson, it may be done reluctantly<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=16&verse=16'>Jdg 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=16&verse=17'>Jdg 16:17</a><p/>Like the sin of Ahab, it may be prompted by others<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=7'>1Ki 21:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=20'>1Ki 21:20</a><p/>Like the sin of Belshazzar it may be done under the influence of strong<p/>drink<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=1'>Dan 5:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=2'>Dan 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=5&verse=27'>Dan 5:27</a><p/>Like the sin of Herod, it may be the result of a foolish promise<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=6'>Mt 14:6-10</a><p/>Like the sin of Judas, it may have the approval of the authorities<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=10'>Mar 14:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=11'>Mar 14:11</a><p/>Like the sin of Pilate, it may be done to gratify the public<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=15'>Mr 15:15</a><p/>Like the sin of the Jews, it may be done in ignorance<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=34'>Lu 23:34</a>"}]}